1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Brands lose time when every new asset restarts the same decisions.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Codex Design Studio starts with intent, audience, and outcome.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Reference evidence stays attributed, rights-aware, and reviewable.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:28,000
GPT-5.6 turns that evidence into one living, versioned Design System.

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:40,000
The polished Web output is directly editable, with stable design nodes and autosave.

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Select a real component and ask Codex to change the source—not a mockup.

7
00:00:53,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Before promotion, the Studio renders the candidate and surfaces any regression.

8
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:08,000
The user keeps the final decision; accepted work remains traceable and reversible.

9
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:15,000
The same system drives editable presentation scenes, not flattened screenshots.

10
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:23,500
Export Web, editable PPTX, and tokens from one governed source of truth.
